  lines:
  - "Hi Dad, seems I\u2019m scheduled to be evacuated today!"
  - "But it doesn\u2019t seem I\u2019ll be going through the booth your stationed
    at, unfortunately. :("
  - "Oh, but some of the kids I\u2019ve been helping out are going through aswell
    today."
  - "If you see Yulian or Susana, they\u2019ll be all clean, and you can let them
    through right away."
  - "Hopefully you get sent through soon, I can\u2019t wait to see you!"
  - And have a great shift today!
